SHIFT + ZZ = Save and Quit vim

fengxinbao@ubuntu:~/transfiles$ vim a.md  # CTRL + ZZ

[1]+  Stopped                 vim a.md
fengxinbao@ubuntu:~/transfiles$ jobs
[1]+  Stopped                 vim a.md
fengxinbao@ubuntu:~/transfiles$ fg 1



